	(1, 2, 'Veronica Corningstone', 'She is an antagonist In Anchorman: The legend of Ron Burgundy and soon a protagonist in Anchorman 2: The legend continues. Veronica Corningstone is played by Christina Applegate ( Married with kids , Don''t tell mom the babysitter is dead)', ' Good evening, San Diego. I''m Veronica Corningstone. Tits McGee is on vacation.'),
